MIT License

Project: Sentry Batch
Version: 1.0.0
Copyright (c) 2026 Kamol Khaeonkhonsim

Sentry Batch is an open-source browser-based IP Threat Intelligence and
Reputation Analysis Console. It enables security analysts to perform
batch investigations against multiple threat intelligence providers,
generate investigation reports, and visualize security data entirely
within the browser.

Repository:
https://github.com/kamolkns/sentrybatch

